**ARGENSOFT INGENIERIA INFORMATICA**
**MENU PRINCIPAL**
SET TALK OFF
SET CONFIRM ON
SET BELL ON
SET SAFETY OFF
STORE 0 TO OP
USE AGE_BASE INDEX AGE_COD
DO WHILE OP <> 6
CLEAR
@1,1 TO 22,78 DOUBLE
@3,24 SAY "ARGENSOFT INGENIERIA INFORMATICA"
@4,31 SAY "AGENDA DE CLIENTES"
@2,21 TO 5,59 
@8,36 SAY '1 - ALTAS'
@10,36 SAY '2 - BAJAS'
@12,36 SAY '3 - MODIFICAR'
@14,36 SAY '4 - LISTADO'
@16,36 SAY '5 - IMPRIMIR'
@18,36 SAY '6 - TERMINAR'
@21,2 SAY 'INGRESE OPCION:'GET OP PICTURE '9'
@21,46 SAY 'Derechos Reservados de A.I.I.' 
READ
DO CASE
CASE OP=1
        DO ALTAS
CASE OP=2
        DO BAJAS
CASE OP=3
        DO MODIF
CASE OP=4 
        DO LISTA
CASE OP=5
        DO IMPRE
CASE OP=6
        EXIT
OTHERWHISE
         @23,18 SAY 'OPCION INCORRECTA... PULSE CUALQUIER TECLA'¨

         WAIT
         @23,0
ENDCASE
ENDDO
CLEAR ALL
CLEAR
